## Summary
This documentation covers Amplitude Experiment's Python SDK for server-side feature flag evaluation, supporting both remote evaluation (fetching variants via API) and local evaluation (client-side evaluation with flag config polling), including cohort targeting, assignment tracking, and Amplitude cookie integration.

